{"tid":356581,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[一語中的] 希治閣巴打一句講中連登仔痛處","createTime":"2017-08-12T07:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T08:28:07.000Z","uid":7397,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ec8656cf8c00dcfb35b330276b6a975015a698","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:52:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/avxpimAPkUo?t=437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FavxpimAPkUo%3Ft%3D437&d=1P3sp5kVsOiNtwDcUNde8%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=01309a3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/avxpimAPkUo?t=437</a><br />\n<br />\n連登仔成日都係批鬥乜乜柒柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當畀人反駁嘅時候 <br />\n次次都會拋一句出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">講馬唔通要快過隻馬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n講真平時又有幾多人真係對批評果樣野有研究吖?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者你地會覺得網上講野冇責任 或者真係唔洗負責任<br />\n不過 的的確確有啲就會因為呢啲批評 而覺得自己再努力都得唔到認同而放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實所謂批評本身冇問題 不過真係要有&quot;評&quot;先算一個有質素嘅&quot;批評 否則只會淪為批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝大家入嚟睇個POST 最後都希望大家<span style=\"color: red;\">就算見到肥絲大隻入嚟都唔會REPLY佢任何野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"fe1b85d6cbdd7b5ff969aa380406b6305b9163dd","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T07:59:43.000Z","msg":"如果對上面講嘅野唔滿意 歡迎大家<span style=\"color: red;\">批評</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都希望大家推下POST 令更多連登仔由今日知道咩叫 <span style=\"color: red;\">批評</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caf1f1de4ee2b443fbae2cf019f343173930ba4","tid":356581,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔不嬲都係垃圾"},{"pid":"14d32c9a653d5618ea073b6cf581cdaf29f2d7cb","tid":356581,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"邊撚個希治閣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9af1d1513120e8b5a0356449c455385a0c55977","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔不嬲都係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n嗱 垃圾都好 要有POINT地批評呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好又批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dc3c6158496c9f964eb7bb0de5fcde55209bcb","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊撚個希治閣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個冇問題 你知佢講緊咩咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a12bcc4ef73480aa87cc9206dddc76f7156ac4","tid":356581,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:07:00.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔會睇到<br />\n佢哋只會為踩而踩, 滿足自我<br />\n唔係為咗搵真相<br />\n同香港人文化一樣"},{"pid":"e5b96f020b4041e5c63b3b9f203dcaf38b8100f4","tid":356581,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊撚個希治閣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個冇問題 你知佢講緊咩咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友咪又係索尼隻狗<br />\n日日批鬥ms 任天堂<br />\n又咩資格講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5568468c40fd3f963a0e9f05ff0b8ae306d415f4","tid":356581,"uid":126286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:08:54.000Z","msg":"用批評既態度去批評人地既批評是否適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f839053f94daf7fe424d44a2ee55e1abda322d0","tid":356581,"uid":67324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:09:19.000Z","msg":"連登仔大把人為屌而屌，好多人都未清楚哂成件事就屌左先，愈來愈似大陸d網民"},{"pid":"94fa0534ac092ff32bd55281dc11ede234ae51ac","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:12:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊撚個希治閣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個冇問題 你知佢講緊咩咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友咪又係索尼隻狗<br />\n日日批鬥ms 任天堂<br />\n又咩資格講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係講嘅野 係唔係有道理先 <br />\n一句野有冇道理應該要由句野嘅內容去分別<br />\n而唔係因為個人嘅做事風格去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f689178617c6d060151972787827abba728d32","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用批評既態度去批評人地既批評是否適合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老老豆豆 批評呢個作為本身唔係問題 只要你有批有評就OK 但係只批不評嘅唔係&quot;批評&quot;<br />\n<br />\n果種常見嘅&quot;批評&quot;方式<span style=\"color: red;\">只係批鬥</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1a212b309ed5255b078d90506f895816f00cfe","tid":356581,"uid":24282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"把聲好難聽<br />\n<br />\n死啦我好似無對人發聲方面有研究<br />\n<br />\nsorry"},{"pid":"6b8fa75a7a860e80f18abd0edbc255884028fc28","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:18:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>把聲好難聽<br />\n<br />\n死啦我好似無對人發聲方面有研究<br />\n<br />\nsorry</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打入嚟 做最佳反面教材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a27a8c3b0e7295416cb1e07fa62d26d139bf8e2","tid":356581,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"「跑得快過馬」呢句係應對另一個歪理「你咁勁又唔自己去做」針對呢句係冇錯到只係被濫用左<br />\n講馬人真係唔洗跑快過隻馬 但要識馬 評價要有理 完"},{"pid":"6132da113aed6740e2285710162126e0fe93bef7","tid":356581,"uid":7397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「跑得快過馬」呢句係應對另一個歪理「你咁勁又唔自己去做」針對呢句係冇錯到只係被濫用左<br />\n講馬人真係唔洗跑快過隻馬 但要識馬 評價要有理 完</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5621f475cdb81d083fc0795aed241c76cceaff","tid":356581,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊撚個希治閣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個冇問題 你知佢講緊咩咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條友咪又係索尼隻狗<br />\n日日批鬥ms 任天堂<br />\n又咩資格講呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係講嘅野 係唔係有道理先 <br />\n一句野有冇道理應該要由句野嘅內容去分別<br />\n而唔係因為個人嘅做事風格去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己講呢句野<br />\n自己都做唔到<br />\n同'講馬唔通要快過隻馬咩'呢個心態有咩分別"}]}